", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2930183302292813e-74, \"text\": \"Jim Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Brown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Same height.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Forty pounds lighter.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smooth gait, at least to observers, but certainly not to anyone attempting to tackle him.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both presented power and speed, peril within grace.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Imagine if Holloway put on the weight he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d need to play professional football.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d look a lot like \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 A.J.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.J._Soprano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.797734612021212e-18, \"text\": \"A.J.\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.J._Soprano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A.J._Soprano\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brown \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and with even more speed.\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Holloway grew from that kid into a large, muscled man among other large, muscled men, Moses knew he had to meet him.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 941, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t specialize in the same event\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Moses won 122-straight 400-meter hurdle races; Holloway triumphs in the shorter hurdles races (60 meters, 110 meters), often finishing races in less time than it takes to fold a T-shirt.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet, from 2021 through mid-\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009824, all anyone seemed to want to ask Holloway about was thatotherOlympic final, three years ago, where he \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009clost\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d gold by 0.05 seconds.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hadn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t dropped a major race since.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not once inthree years.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The last person to dominate a hurdle discipline like that?\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moses.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He wanted to see Holloway\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s size, because Moses could already ascertain the depth of technical skill.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re the same height.\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both had to figure out ways to, Moses says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cregulate\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d their strides.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 110-meter version, the hurdle is taller, but principles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094of physics, aerodynamics and responses to both\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094are applied in similar ways.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meet, they did\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094on May 31, at the Edwin Moses Legends Meet, roughly two months before Holloway would hunt for that elusive gold.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moses takes it from there.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd, my God,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Moses says in Paris.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2134, \"end\": 2139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0438582812395075e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t know how big he was, his size, anything like that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  He found Holloway larger, more muscular and more imposing than expected\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and he expected to find Holloway large, muscular and imposing.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2219, \"end\": 2227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}, {\"begin\": 2308, \"end\": 2316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t built like an NFL wideout.\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2373, \"end\": 2376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.454516384536502e-14, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was built like an NFLpractice facility.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But even more than that, Moses noticed something else.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway was also built to run one specific race.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s custom-made to run those hurdles,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Moses says.\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He laughs.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIf Grant hits a hurdle, that hurdle is \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6going down.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He laughs again, harder this time.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2611, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6185418063524317e-23, \"text\": \"Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d hate to get in the way of his forearm.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Upon arrival in France, Holloway described himself as a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csore loser.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He even remembered the last time that anyone had beaten him in a competition \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 last September.\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2768, \"end\": 2774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9220658364556084, \"rank\": 0.08415351057634358, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2776, \"end\": 2784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moses understood that mindset.\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in an Olympics, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d rather finishsevenththan second.\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 3014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou get your ass kicked.\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3042, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You move on.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Holloway grew up in Chesapeake, Va.\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3060, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}, {\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chesapeake_Bay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.889359475973996e-20, \"text\": \"Chesapeake\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chesapeake_Bay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chesapeake_Bay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t exactly a born hurdler.\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, if he was, that wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t clear yet.\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athleticism reigned.\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He played several sports and often with Stan, a retired officer in the U.S. Navy, as coach.\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3269, \"end\": 3273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Navy_Midshipmen_football\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.36354545337492e-12, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Navy_Midshipmen_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Navy_Midshipmen_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around age 15, Grant\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s body started to develop.\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tall, fast and strong, he would gain weight for football and lose it for track.\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His father didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t mind the variety.\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But in Grant, around that age, he saw what Moses would see later\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a body that all but screamedelite hurdler.\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3461, \"end\": 3466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6185418063524317e-23, \"text\": \"Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulysses_S._Grant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eventually, Grant whittled his athletic ambitions to track and football.\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In track, he sprinted, hurdled, high jumped and long jumped.\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He trained at the Track 757 club, where Stan was an assistant coach.\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In football, Grant played receiver and defensive back for Grassfield High.\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dozens of offers pour into the school\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s athletics office\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Clemson, Tennessee, Michigan and the Bulldogs, of course.\", \"from\": 3843, \"to\": 3961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3913, \"end\": 3922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennessee_Volunteers_football\", \"score\": 0.9999999797209969, \"rank\": 2.0273801238863046e-08, \"text\": \"Tennessee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennessee_Volunteers_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennessee_Volunteers_football\"}, {\"begin\": 3924, \"end\": 3932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan_Wolverines_football\", \"score\": 0.9999999980891516, \"rank\": 1.9064830764699706e-09, \"text\": \"Michigan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan_Wolverines_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan_Wolverines_football\"}, {\"begin\": 3941, \"end\": 3949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\", \"score\": 0.9999992817804774, \"rank\": 7.16672828861028e-07, \"text\": \"Bulldogs\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many wanted him to compete in both.\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway did not.\", \"from\": 3999, \"to\": 4016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3999, \"end\": 4007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He decided he liked competing byhimself, the most significant factor in a close and difficult decision.\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He chose Florida for college, but not to score touchdowns in The Swamp.\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4130, \"end\": 4137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"score\": 0.9999907690751979, \"rank\": 9.222201333022656e-06, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wanted to run for Mike Holloway (no relation).\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4214, \"end\": 4227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Holloway\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9101131882120255e-36, \"text\": \"Mike Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This season marked his 22nd as the university\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s track coach, where SEC championships are the minimum expectation and national titles the real prize.\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4320, \"end\": 4323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeastern_Conference\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9598907915955565e-16, \"text\": \"SEC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeastern_Conference\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeastern_Conference\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, they won three national championships at UF; Holloway eight individual crowns.\", \"from\": 4403, \"to\": 4491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4454, \"end\": 4456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.223135453658538e-24, \"text\": \"UF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cFlorida took him to a whole \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098nother level,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Stan says.\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4495, \"end\": 4502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"score\": 0.9999907690751979, \"rank\": 9.222201333022656e-06, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cCoach Holloway had started something Grant just needed to finish.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  It didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t take Grant long to level up.\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4563, \"end\": 4571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He turned pro and kept winning.\", \"from\": 4668, \"to\": 4699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They called him the Wonder Boy, and the Wonder Boy left UF in 2019.\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4740, \"end\": 4750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wonder_Boy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8266463423950217e-28, \"text\": \"Wonder Boy\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wonder_Boy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wonder_Boy\"}, {\"begin\": 4756, \"end\": 4758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.223135453658538e-24, \"text\": \"UF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Florida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the five years since, he won three world championships, one Diamond League final and that silver medal that felt more like a loss.\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4831, \"end\": 4845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.834701438770078e-21, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year alone, he erased a 30-year-old indoor world record in the 60-meter hurdles, finishing in 7.29 seconds and clocked a 12.81-second 110 in the U.S. Olympic trials, good for the second-fastest time, ever, in that discipline.\", \"from\": 4902, \"to\": 5132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He held the fourth-fastest time (12.86) too.\", \"from\": 5133, \"to\": 5177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the 13 times in track history that a hurdler broke 13 seconds at that distance, 10 of those are his marks.\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Told of the praise from Moses, Holloway\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s face twisted in something like surprise.\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He praised the legend right back, then delivered an answer that was neither braggadocious nor subtle.\", \"from\": 5374, \"to\": 5475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cUm, do I feel I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m dominant?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he said.\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cUh, yes.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Proof: in Paris, Holloway breezed through his heats.\", \"from\": 5521, \"to\": 5589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5547, \"end\": 5552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0438582812395075e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5554, \"end\": 5562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his semifinal, he ran a 12.98 seconds.\", \"from\": 5590, \"to\": 5631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That would have won gold, too.\", \"from\": 5632, \"to\": 5662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He won the final in 12.99.\", \"from\": 5663, \"to\": 5689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Redemption?\", \"from\": 5690, \"to\": 5701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At last?No way, Holloway told reporters.\", \"from\": 5702, \"to\": 5742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5718, \"end\": 5726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When an athlete like Holloway wins a gold medal like he won his in Paris, the spotlight descends with a glorious fury.\", \"from\": 5744, \"to\": 5862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5765, \"end\": 5773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}, {\"begin\": 5811, \"end\": 5816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0438582812395075e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cameras trained on Holloway late Thursday, as did millions of eyeballs and thousands of cell phones cameras at Stade de France.\", \"from\": 5863, \"to\": 5990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5882, \"end\": 5890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}, {\"begin\": 5974, \"end\": 5989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 5974, \"end\": 5989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beats thumped.\", \"from\": 5991, \"to\": 6005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then came the hugs, pounds and hi-fives; the deluge of praise; and the endless interviews.\", \"from\": 6006, \"to\": 6096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two days later, he still looked a little tired from the less-immediate aftermath.\", \"from\": 6098, \"to\": 6179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about that longer aftermath and any detail he might provide, Holloway chose a more immediate moment instead.\", \"from\": 6180, \"to\": 6294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6247, \"end\": 6255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had heard about the bell that winners (and only winners) rang inside the stadium.\", \"from\": 6295, \"to\": 6379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That it will later be placed in Notre Dame Cathedral.\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That sentiment stuck with him.\", \"from\": 6434, \"to\": 6464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m part of history here in Paris,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he said.\", \"from\": 6466, \"to\": 6517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6499, \"end\": 6504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0438582812395075e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also said the enormity of his triumph had yet to hit him.\", \"from\": 6519, \"to\": 6579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He plans to sit outside, once home in Florida, sip some tea or maybe allow for a glass of wine, and reflect.\", \"from\": 6580, \"to\": 6688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6618, \"end\": 6625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"score\": 0.9999907690751979, \"rank\": 9.222201333022656e-06, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_Gators_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only then will he see what bubbles up.\", \"from\": 6689, \"to\": 6727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chances are, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll consider his now-famous arc.\", \"from\": 6729, \"to\": 6778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday night, at Stade de France, Stan and Latasha Holloway stood near the section where parents of U.S. athletes sit.\", \"from\": 6780, \"to\": 6903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6802, \"end\": 6817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 6836, \"end\": 6844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their son would compete in 30 minutes, in another Olympic final, the one that wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t necessary to confirm his dominance\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and yet, also the one that would eliminate any final slivers of doubt remaining.\", \"from\": 6904, \"to\": 7108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone nearby wanted pictures.\", \"from\": 7110, \"to\": 7142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They opened with, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYour son is awesome,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou guys are awesome.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d What the Holloways wanted was for Grant tobeawesome, on that purple track, and not for them but for him, to end this particular narrative.\", \"from\": 7143, \"to\": 7359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It centered on the silver medal he won at the last Games.\", \"from\": 7360, \"to\": 7417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On that day, he didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t feel like he \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cwon\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d anything.\", \"from\": 7418, \"to\": 7475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s race was the final event on the third-to-last day of the Paris Games.Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone had just set a world recordin the 400-meter hurdles.\", \"from\": 7477, \"to\": 7637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, it was Holloway\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s turn.\", \"from\": 7638, \"to\": 7668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the gun sounded, his start wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t ideal.\", \"from\": 7670, \"to\": 7715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But his steps were, and that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what mattered.\", \"from\": 7716, \"to\": 7763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway sailed over hurdles, gaining speed, creating space between himself and the rest of the field.\", \"from\": 7764, \"to\": 7866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7764, \"end\": 7772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every movement was equal parts Muscle Beach powerful and Prius efficient.\", \"from\": 7867, \"to\": 7940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7898, \"end\": 7910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muscle_Beach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1084596627051947e-30, \"text\": \"Muscle Beach\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muscle_Beach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muscle_Beach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hurdle.\", \"from\": 7941, \"to\": 7948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three steps.\", \"from\": 7949, \"to\": 7961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hurdle.\", \"from\": 7962, \"to\": 7969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three steps.\", \"from\": 7970, \"to\": 7982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All the way through the finish line.\", \"from\": 7983, \"to\": 8019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes.\", \"from\": 8021, \"to\": 8025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To understand why, context matters.\", \"from\": 8026, \"to\": 8061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As do two literal steps.\", \"from\": 8062, \"to\": 8086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That Tokyo performance wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t a disappointment.\", \"from\": 8088, \"to\": 8137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8093, \"end\": 8098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999997305203941, \"rank\": 2.6947923393561197e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not to anyone but Holloway.\", \"from\": 8138, \"to\": 8165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8156, \"end\": 8164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone near him in the mixed zone, where interviews are conducted in airport security-style lines with steel barricades, will never forget one particular exchange.\", \"from\": 8166, \"to\": 8329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t disappointed.\", \"from\": 8331, \"to\": 8362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8331, \"end\": 8339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, he was far more heated than that.\", \"from\": 8363, \"to\": 8400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was angry, as if someone had rushed onto the track and added matchbox cars, sand burrs and broken glass in only his lane.\", \"from\": 8401, \"to\": 8525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam Kilgore ofThe Washington Postgently pointed out the obvious.\", \"from\": 8526, \"to\": 8591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8531, \"end\": 8538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.141558271309271e-22, \"text\": \"Kilgore\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway was 23 years old then.\", \"from\": 8592, \"to\": 8623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8592, \"end\": 8600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had just won a silver medal at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 8624, \"to\": 8671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gap between him and gold was infinitely smaller than it took Kilgore to ask his question.\", \"from\": 8672, \"to\": 8765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8737, \"end\": 8744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.141558271309271e-22, \"text\": \"Kilgore\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hadn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t yet received his medal.\", \"from\": 8766, \"to\": 8801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He looked like he didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want it.\", \"from\": 8802, \"to\": 8837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The silver medalist scanned the reporters huddled in around him, separated by a barricade.\", \"from\": 8839, \"to\": 8929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He asked them how they might feel if they were, say, the second-best writer in the world.\", \"from\": 8930, \"to\": 9019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Heads scanned.\", \"from\": 9020, \"to\": 9034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shoulders raised.\", \"from\": 9035, \"to\": 9052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Consensus: pretty freaking good.\", \"from\": 9053, \"to\": 9085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not how Holloway is wired.\", \"from\": 9087, \"to\": 9122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9104, \"end\": 9112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not how he competes or why.\\u00c2  Moses saw something in the way Holloway races.\", \"from\": 9123, \"to\": 9199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Typically, he wins or loses based on two steps.\", \"from\": 9200, \"to\": 9247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The very first two he makes, in fact.\", \"from\": 9248, \"to\": 9285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps that sounds like an exaggeration, but Stan Holloway, Grant\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s father, confirmed what Moses saw on Thursday night at Stade de France.\", \"from\": 9286, \"to\": 9427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9337, \"end\": 9345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}, {\"begin\": 9411, \"end\": 9426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 9411, \"end\": 9426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHis first two steps are the most important,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Moses says.\", \"from\": 9429, \"to\": 9490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBefore he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s even taking off, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s where the rubber meets the road for him.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Speed isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t exactly the issue there.\", \"from\": 9491, \"to\": 9617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Timing and rhythm shape success or failure.\", \"from\": 9618, \"to\": 9661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t gingerly tiptoe into a race.\", \"from\": 9662, \"to\": 9710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9662, \"end\": 9670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t start so slow as to fade from contention.\", \"from\": 9711, \"to\": 9770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But those steps assume paramount importance because of all theothersteps that follow them.\", \"from\": 9771, \"to\": 9861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway is so big, in an event where the distance is so short, that he must begin 110-hurdle races with precisely the right timing.\", \"from\": 9862, \"to\": 9994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9862, \"end\": 9870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What only someone like Moses or Stan Holloway would know is that elite hurdlers typically don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ccount\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d their first step of the race.\", \"from\": 9996, \"to\": 10135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10033, \"end\": 10041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They make it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094andthenthey begin counting.\", \"from\": 10136, \"to\": 10178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They leap the first barrier and ideally take exactly the same amount of steps before they leap again.\", \"from\": 10179, \"to\": 10280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Holloway\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s case, in that particular race, three steps, taken in precisely the right spots on the track, after every hurdle\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the ideal.\", \"from\": 10281, \"to\": 10430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first two matter, because they determine how he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll clear every hurdle down the track, all the way through the last one.\", \"from\": 10432, \"to\": 10557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If he gets out too fast, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s more likely to clip a hurdle through momentum alone.\", \"from\": 10558, \"to\": 10642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If he gets out too slowly, he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s more likely to try and pick up his pace, which is most often done by extending one\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s stride.\", \"from\": 10643, \"to\": 10771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moses says this is natural\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094as in, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s human nature to try and catch up.\", \"from\": 10772, \"to\": 10848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not the right correction.\", \"from\": 10849, \"to\": 10890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe only place you can regulate,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Moses says, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cis right there.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d At the beginning.\", \"from\": 10891, \"to\": 10981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Told all this, Stan smiles and furiously nods his head.\", \"from\": 10983, \"to\": 11038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, his son was the reigning world champion and the favorite.\", \"from\": 11039, \"to\": 11106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11042, \"end\": 11047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999997305203941, \"rank\": 2.6947923393561197e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that start did not separate Holloway from the pack, as typically happens when he races.\", \"from\": 11107, \"to\": 11198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11139, \"end\": 11147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His rhythm was off, right away.\", \"from\": 11199, \"to\": 11230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, Holloway pulled ahead by the 60-meter mark.\", \"from\": 11231, \"to\": 11281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11238, \"end\": 11246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t mistakeleadingforrhythm.\", \"from\": 11282, \"to\": 11319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He clipped the seventh hurdle, broke form and leapt over the final three barriers from a jump point that wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t obvious to the casual eye but was, to those who understand the hurdles, far too close.\", \"from\": 11320, \"to\": 11520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When a hurdler doesthat, they lose momentum.\", \"from\": 11521, \"to\": 11565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re jumpingupward, even just a little.\", \"from\": 11566, \"to\": 11610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And when they do that, they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re notjumping forward, which is up but not the same.\", \"from\": 11611, \"to\": 11693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009c[Those] steps dictate if I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to win that race or not,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Holloway says.\", \"from\": 11695, \"to\": 11777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11763, \"end\": 11771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He copped to \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cGod-given ability\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d that allows him, sometimes, to recover where others would not.\\u00c2  That he still nabbed a silver medal and almost won anyway, spoke not to failure, but to Holloway\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s immense gifts.\", \"from\": 11778, \"to\": 11995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two steps.\", \"from\": 11996, \"to\": 12006, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s all that cost him gold.\", \"from\": 12007, \"to\": 12039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, Holloway understood that how fast he ran mattered\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094of course, it did\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094but only running the right wayandfast would net him what he wanted most.\", \"from\": 12041, \"to\": 12195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12044, \"end\": 12049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0438582812395075e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 12051, \"end\": 12059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was fast in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 12196, \"to\": 12217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12211, \"end\": 12216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999997305203941, \"rank\": 2.6947923393561197e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also staggered through his step and even turned his head near the finish line.\", \"from\": 12218, \"to\": 12299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a race decided by 0.05 seconds, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s enough to lose.\", \"from\": 12300, \"to\": 12359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Late Thursday he said he actually cramped in Paris, near the end of his face, maybe at hurdle No.\", \"from\": 12361, \"to\": 12458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12406, \"end\": 12411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0438582812395075e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"9.\", \"from\": 12459, \"to\": 12461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When pressed as to which leg cramped, he responded,Both.\", \"from\": 12462, \"to\": 12518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The difference was he already led by a large enough margin to withstand it.\", \"from\": 12519, \"to\": 12594, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What gave him that lead?\", \"from\": 12596, \"to\": 12620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those first two steps, of course.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI won an Olympic gold medal,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Holloway says.\", \"from\": 12621, \"to\": 12706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12692, \"end\": 12700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo I [would] say they were pretty damn good.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Still, that might not have been obvious.\", \"from\": 12707, \"to\": 12799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t shoot from the starting blocks like a low-trajectory human rocket.\", \"from\": 12800, \"to\": 12878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, his teammate, silver medal winner Daniel Roberts, left the gate ahead.\", \"from\": 12879, \"to\": 12958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12922, \"end\": 12936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Roberts_(fighter)\", \"score\": 0.9171939871993402, \"rank\": 0.050154320987637786, \"text\": \"Daniel Roberts\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Roberts_(fighter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Roberts_(fighter)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Holloway didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t need to win the first 10 meters.\", \"from\": 12959, \"to\": 13009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12959, \"end\": 12967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He needed toregulatehis stride and not fall too far behind.\", \"from\": 13010, \"to\": 13069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He did both.\", \"from\": 13070, \"to\": 13082, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, the world record holder in the 60-meter hurdles turned on that afterburner speed.\", \"from\": 13083, \"to\": 13170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t break the world record.\", \"from\": 13172, \"to\": 13207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But few in track and field think he won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t ever break it.\", \"from\": 13208, \"to\": 13266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By late Thursday, Holloway had completed track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s version of a grand slam.\", \"from\": 13268, \"to\": 13343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13286, \"end\": 13294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued to say it wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t redemptive, Olympic gold, but he also said he felt relief at having ended all the questions that persisted, nagging at him, once and for all.\", \"from\": 13344, \"to\": 13517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Which sure sounded a lot like redemption, no?\", \"from\": 13518, \"to\": 13563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless, Holloway has entered rare territory.\", \"from\": 13565, \"to\": 13613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13577, \"end\": 13585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s on a similar trajectory to Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone.\", \"from\": 13614, \"to\": 13674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13648, \"end\": 13654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.999972150334907, \"rank\": 2.785009643853882e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not as far along as she is in terms of changing what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s possible for short-distance hurdlers.\", \"from\": 13675, \"to\": 13776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But what tethers both is who they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re racing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094not humans but history and the clock.\", \"from\": 13777, \"to\": 13862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Holloway says his plan is to win at least one major championship medal every year.\", \"from\": 13864, \"to\": 13951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13869, \"end\": 13877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.801018717952144e-12, \"text\": \"Holloway\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q40357\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HM_Prison_Holloway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will give new meaning to the cliched question, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhat do you want?\", \"from\": 13952, \"to\": 14024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A medal?\\u00e2\\u0080